      <title>证明人以 1 亿欧元贷款支持 Signa Prime 重组</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-29/attestor-backs-signa-prime-restructuring-with-100-million-loan</link>
      <description><![CDATA[扭亏为盈的专业投资者 Attestor Ltd 将向 Signa 破产的豪华地产部门提供高达 1 亿欧元（1.08 亿美元）的贷款，这是避免该公司破产时资产抛售的关键一步。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-29/attestor-backs-signa-prime-restructuring-with-100-million-loan</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 29 Mar 2024 11:51:40 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>韩国银行表示将向投资者赔偿与中国相关的票据</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-29/korean-banks-say-to-compensate-investors-for-china-linked-notes</link>
      <description><![CDATA[一些韩国银行同意赔偿因与中国股票相关的结构性产品而遭受损失的投资者，而就在几周前，当局称其中一些银行在销售时歪曲了这些复杂的工具。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-29/korean-banks-say-to-compensate-investors-for-china-linked-notes</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 29 Mar 2024 10:25:09 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>波兰通胀 36 个月来首次降至目标</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-29/poland-s-inflation-drops-to-target-for-first-time-in-36-months</link>
      <description><![CDATA[尽管由于担心 2024 年晚些时候物价增长复苏，政策制定者预计将保持利率稳定，但 3 月份波兰通胀率三年来首次降至央行目标。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-29/poland-s-inflation-drops-to-target-for-first-time-in-36-months</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 29 Mar 2024 09:22:22 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>尼日利亚要求银行将最低资本提高至 3.59 亿美元</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-29/nigeria-tells-banks-to-raise-minimum-capital-to-359-million</link>
      <description><![CDATA[尼日利亚央行将贷款机构的最低资本要求提高了 10 倍，以加强对面临奈拉大幅贬值、高通胀和经济疲软的行业的防御。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-29/nigeria-tells-banks-to-raise-minimum-capital-to-359-million</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 29 Mar 2024 08:43:06 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>先正达等待三年后撤回中国IPO申请</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-29/syngenta-plans-to-withdraw-china-ipo-application-on-weak-market</link>
      <description><![CDATA[先正达集团撤回了拖延已久的在上海进行 90 亿美元首次公开募股的申请，这是继阿里巴巴集团控股有限公司本周取消其物流部门上市后对中国股市的又一次打击。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-29/syngenta-plans-to-withdraw-china-ipo-application-on-weak-market</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 29 Mar 2024 08:34:16 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
