      <title>花旗策略师下调美国科技股评级，因涨势扩大</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-29/citi-strategists-downgrade-us-tech-stocks-as-rally-to-broaden</link>
      <description><![CDATA[花旗集团策略师表示，美国股市的涨势将扩大到科技以外的领域，他们对该行业的前景变得更加谨慎。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-29/citi-strategists-downgrade-us-tech-stocks-as-rally-to-broaden</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 29 Mar 2024 08:09:54 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
